{"title":"VPM翻墙","date":"2018-12-31T07:34:36.000Z","slug":"ShadowSocks翻墙","tags":["ShadowSocks"],"updated":"2018-12-31T08:03:21.468Z","content":"<h3 id=\"ShadowSocks翻墙教程\"><a href=\"#ShadowSocks翻墙教程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ShadowSocks翻墙教程\"></a>ShadowSocks翻墙教程</h3><h4 id=\"购买服务器\"><a href=\"#购买服务器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"购买服务器\"></a>购买服务器</h4><ul>\n<li><code>Linode</code></li>\n<li><code>DigitalOcean</code></li>\n<li><code>BandwagonHOST</code></li>\n<li><code>vultr</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"安装SSR\"><a href=\"#安装SSR\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装SSR\"></a>安装SSR</h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install wget -y //如果没有wget先安装</span><br><span class=\"line\">wget --no-check-certificate https://freed.ga/github/shadowsocksR.sh; bash shadowsocksR.sh //安装ssr脚本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>接下来根据提示设置SSR连接信息，配置完成后就可以下载shadowsocksR客户端进行连接，手机可以使用ShadowRocket小火箭<br><img src=\"http://www.lyz1234.com//userfiles/files/admin/cmd2.jpg\" alt=\"img\"><img src=\"http://www.lyz1234.com//userfiles/files/admin/cmd4.jpg\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"安装BBR加速\"><a href=\"#安装BBR加速\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装BBR加速\"></a>安装BBR加速</h4><ol>\n<li><p>获取Google BBR脚本并执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/teddysun/across/raw/master/bbr.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\">sh ./bbr.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>查看内核版本是否大于4.9</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">uname -r</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>执行<code>sysctl net.ipv4.tcp_available_congestion_control</code>，看是否有返回</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">net.ipv4.tcp_available_congestion_control = reno cubic bbr</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>执行<code>sysctl net.core.default_qdisc</code>，看是否有以下返回</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">net.core.default_qdisc = fq</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>执行<code>lsmod | grep bbr</code>，返回值有<code>tcp_bbr</code>表示已经启动</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装完成后，脚本提示需要重启vps，输入y并回车，重启</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"安装锐速\"><a href=\"#安装锐速\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装锐速\"></a>安装锐速</h4><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget -N --no-check-certificate https://freed.ga/kernel/ruisu.sh &amp;&amp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">bash ruisu.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>脚本安装完之后重启服务器，继续安装</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget -N --no-check-certificate https://github.com/91yun/serverspeeder/raw/master/serverspeeder.sh &amp;&amp; bash serverspeeder.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>备用脚本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget -N --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/91yun/serverspeeder/master/serverspeeder-all.sh &amp;&amp; bash serverspeeder-all.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","next":{"title":"二维码","slug":"二维码"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/ShadowSocks翻墙/"}